values.name: Mission
values.description: At Blueprint, members are unified under our mission to amplify impact where technology solutions make sense and drive positive change.

values.name: Quality
values.description: Projects are carefully selected to create lasting impact, and our teams treat all projects with the utmost care and integrity.

values.name: Growth
values.description: Members are invested in each other's academic, professional, and social growth. We seek to sustain a continuous cycle of learning and teaching.

values.name: Community
values.description: Though our work stems from our passion for technology, we strive to build meaningful relationships that extend well beyond the scope of the organization.
